{"tid":2152738,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西雅圖禁防暴警針對記者救護 不得無差別射催淚彈 即使示威被定性為「暴動」時相關準則亦適用","createTime":"2020-08-12T07:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T07:06:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae62ce69833fdd40d8f969537bf62418ebad019d","tid":2152738,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】美國西雅圖連月爆發反種族主義和反警暴示威，引發嚴重警民衝突，有示威者入稟控告市政府縱容警察在人群管制時使用不必要暴力，剝削公民和平示威的憲法權利，亦對記者及醫護等濫用暴力。當地市政府周一（10日）決定遵從法院命令，不准警察以防暴武器瞄準示威現場的記者、醫護、觀察員，即使示威被當局定性為「暴動」時相關準則亦適用。代表原告的律師形容這令西雅圖成為全美「最全面保護」相關人士的城市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200812/s00014/1597171163183/%E8%A5%BF%E9%9B%85%E5%9C%96%E7%A6%81%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E7%84%A1%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%A5%E5%B0%84%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88-%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200812%2Fs00014%2F1597171163183%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%259B%2585%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%2597%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E5%2588%25A5%25E5%25B0%2584%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf%2FiPq%2FHqG0pMUyXzarzxqBM%3D&h=b7d8ad55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200812%2Fs00014%2F1597171163183%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E9%259B%2585%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%2597